{"tid":728864,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"棄百萬年薪 走遍全港 21歲青年追夢失敗","createTime":"2018-07-04T05:42:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T07:03:05.000Z","uid":125688,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"66cf1366ffd5b33576875b55b508a61345bffaf3","tid":728864,"uid":125688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T05:42:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180704/mobile/bkn-20180704121259939-0704_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180704%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180704121259939-0704_00822_001.html&d=MNrG5JtwMuDYEPeFXOW5BjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=52b47a9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180704/mobile/bkn-20180704121259939-0704_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n21歲仔沙田站亮槍走甩　再闖屯門滙豐銀行被捕<br />\n<br />\n屯門市廣場懷槍客闖銀行被捕，早上(4日)11時許，一名21歲青年進入滙豐銀行聲稱要開戶口，期間突亮出一把手槍，職員大驚立即報警。大批警員迅速趕至，當場將他拘捕，正封鎖現場調查。由於被捕青年的衣着及外形，與今早曾在港鐵沙田站亮槍的疑人相似，警方經調查後，證實為同一人。 <br />\n<br />\n現場消息稱，疑犯被捕時精神紊亂，警方正調查其手槍的真偽。"},{"pid":"dac00c6113ca64e1c1da4cbfb2a8b39903161ec8","tid":728864,"uid":125688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T05:52:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1403bf8011650ed7ccc401dba0b0716472a1f87","tid":728864,"uid":1067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T05:54:20.000Z","msg":"個topic邊度嚟？"},{"pid":"b391b5d3df48f92c7aed6129a91f51631242edfe","tid":728864,"uid":125688,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"b1403bf8011650ed7ccc401dba0b0716472a1f87","tid":728864,"uid":1067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T05:54:20.000Z","msg":"個topic邊度嚟？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T05:57:00.000Z","msg":"佢50歲後應該有百萬年薪，按照每年加3%人工"},{"pid":"4ab117e21c619e31bd435c446b5b31dfd859c8c9","tid":728864,"uid":7903,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T05:57:16.000Z","msg":"Fake 